{"tid":2450070,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊明孖女友莊思明打科興疫苗：多謝中國政府！","createTime":"2021-03-17T06:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T08:13:20.000Z","uid":128369,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ff4bf8537071eda94cba8a48431245d7c2739c","tid":2450070,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎肆虐，政府推行2019冠狀病毒病疫苗接種計劃，向來力撐政府的楊明於周二（16日）就孖女友莊思明一同前往注射國產的科興疫苗不忘打卡，他在個人IG上載注射疫苗後的合照並寫道：「我哋打咗第一針喇，完全冇唔舒服嘅感覺，打之前醫生有講解清楚亦有小冊子提供參考！其實打邊隻疫苗都冇所謂，最緊要大家都健康！為己為人，為抗疫，打疫苗係最有效控制疫情嘅方法。祝大家健康快樂！」他又不忘標籤： #多謝中國政府 #香港特別行政區 #科興 #克爾來福；而女友莊思明亦寫道：「護己護人，齊打疫苗。我哋打咗第一針啦！」<br />\nSource:hk01"},{"pid":"551ee5ef64d0919475a48bfbe0ae8cd62a4d51b2","tid":2450070,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放心打完就黎連感覺都無架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0645bea68cc4f7c11f6a527f7df97c0087874573","tid":2450070,"uid":29947,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"快d打撚死條八婆"},{"pid":"1528aef2ef29269e89cdff1489777a537154bc29","tid":2450070,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0645bea68cc4f7c11f6a527f7df97c0087874573","tid":2450070,"uid":29947,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"快d打撚死條八婆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"又往死裏打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf8972b4f0c7143122defb07f42dc65c156bd74","tid":2450070,"uid":11719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"不如喺背脊刻埋「貞忠報國」丫，乜都要掛住中國喺嘴邊，佢唔覺得好肉酸咩？佢同楊明扑野係咪都會多謝習近平？"},{"pid":"ab47c51e067fa1c639bfd590ee877f60fdded8a4","t